      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior has extensive rust, major paint peeling, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine currently does not start, and there are visible fluid leaks throughout the undercarriage. This is best suited as a dedicated project car or a source for parts.",
